fields.Description: Designed for small to medium-scale operations, this machine delivers excellent performance with its branded components, dual-phase motor, and consistent output over 6 passes. Compact and highly efficient.

The WS125 is a professional-grade single head rolling machine designed for precision in sheet and wire processing. Its compact form factor and dual phase compatibility make it ideal for space-constrained or mobile operations.
KeyPoints: 1.5 HP motor with Single/Three Phase compatibility
Branded electrical components for long life
Reliable performance for light to medium load

fields.Description: This industrial-strength machine is designed for high-volume production environments. The double head configuration allows for multiple operations simultaneously, significantly increasing productivity. Built with premium materials and precision engineering for long-term reliability.
KeyPoints: Double head configuration for increased productivity
Variable speed control with digital display

fields.Description: Built with a robust hydraulic pump and 2 HP motor, this press is ideal for gold and silver embossing and stamping applications. Heavy-duty frame construction ensures reliable long-term use.

The WS125 model offers a reliable solution for small to medium jewelry manufacturers. Its compact design, quality rollers, and dual-phase compatibility make it a preferred choice for precision rolling of gold and silver sheets or wires.
This manual bench draw machine is built with a solid base and precision alignment to offer exceptional control for pulling gold and silver wires. Optional motorization available.
Perfect for workshops needing both wire and sheet rolling. Two-head mechanism improves workflow and versatility.

The WSD125 is purpose-built for advanced jewelry chain-making needs, offering high-precision rolls shaped for square, triangle, and hollow profiles. VFD control ensures smooth operation and precise output quality, making it ideal for both artisan and industrial use.
KeyPoints: Variable Frequency Drive (VFD) for speed control
Double head design for high output

fields.Description: Built with a stronger frame and wider roller mounts for precise dual-mode operation. Great for continuous light industrial usage.
Best for heavier sheet or thicker wire applications, this model offers stability, precision, and industrial-grade performance.
Fitted with hardened D3 rollers and a high-torque motor, SD150 delivers efficient performance across gold, silver, and harder alloys.
Designed for workshops requiring speed, strength, and lubrication automation, this machine delivers precision for wire and sheet rolling.
Ideal for workshops that require consistent high-speed rolling with minimal maintenance, offering dual speed motor and hardened rollers.
Heavy-duty build for continuous operation. Supports multiple wire roll size options and ideal for precious metals.
Industrial-grade machine designed for high-performance rolling in gold and silver industries. Handles thick wires and sheets with precision.
Engineered for durability and industrial-grade productivity, this machine is ideal for continuous sheet rolling in metal workshops.
Made for large-scale operations, SS300 provides precision rolling with a powerful 10HP motor and durable components for long-term use.
Built with a robust hydraulic pump and 2 HP motor, this press is ideal for gold and silver embossing and stamping applications. Heavy-duty frame construction ensures reliable long-term use.
Equipped with a heavy-duty hydraulic pump and 3 HP motor, this press ensures high pressure precision pressing with safety and efficiency in high-volume workflows.

This state-of-the-art wire drawing machine incorporates advanced automation technology to deliver consistent, high-quality wire reduction. The 8-pass system allows for significant diameter reduction while maintaining material integrity and surface finish.

The HMI-6 Wire Drawing Machine is a compact, efficient, and reliable solution designed for continuous wire drawing operations. Built with precision and durability in mind, it ensures consistent performance while minimizing maintenance.

The 12 Pass Wire Drawing Machine is designed for high-performance wire drawing operations, combining power, precision, and durability. Equipped with a 3 H.P Three Phase Motor and a 12-die holder, it ensures efficient production with consistent output quality.

The Single Die Wire Drawing Machine is a compact and efficient solution designed for small-scale and precise wire drawing operations. Equipped with a 1.5 H.P motor, this machine ensures reliable performance with low power consumption. Its 1 Die Holder provides consistent wire drawing quality, while the VFD controller allows smooth speed regulation for different production needs.

fields.discription: A jewelry rolling machine, or rolling mill, is a mechanical tool that uses two or more hardened steel rollers to compress and reshape metal at room temperature, a process called cold rolling. It's essential for transforming raw metal into uniform sheets or wires of specific thickness and for imparting textures, making it a versatile instrument for various jewelry-making techniques

fields.title: Revolutionizing Jewelry Manufacturing with Precision Machinery
fields.discription: In today’s fast-paced jewelry industry, precision, automation, and durability are essential for maintaining quality and meeting demand. At Hitesh Malviya Industries, we specialize in manufacturing high-performance jewelry machinery designed to transform traditional production methods.
fields.text:
{"delta":"{\"ops\":[{\"insert\":\"In today’s fast-paced jewelry industry, precision, automation, and durability are essential for maintaining quality and meeting demand. At Hitesh Malviya Industries, we specialize in manufacturing high-performance jewelry machinery designed to transform traditional production methods.\\n\\nOur rolling mills and wire drawing machines are engineered with micron-level accuracy, delivering flawless results for gold, silver, and alloy processing. Each machine is constructed using heavy-duty materials to ensure long-lasting performance, even under continuous operation.\\n\\nBy integrating semi-automatic and motorized systems, we bridge the gap between craftsmanship and technology. Our machines feature smart control systems that increase productivity while minimizing manual labor—making them ideal for modern jewelers.\\n\\nWith over 25 years of experience, we offer customized machinery solutions tailored to specific manufacturing needs. Whether you're a small workshop or a large-scale factory, our equipment is built to improve efficiency and reduce production time.\\n\\nWe also provide global support, including shipping, on-site installation, and after-sales service to ensure seamless operation across borders.\\n\\nWhy Choose Us?\\n\\n✅ Precision-built jewelry machinery\\n🛠️ Crafted with micron-level accuracy for flawless results.\\n\\n💪 Durable and reliable design\\n🔩 Built to withstand continuous, heavy-duty use.\\n\\n⚙️ Automation for efficient production\\n📈 Boosts productivity with minimal manual effort.\\n\\n🧩 Custom solutions for all scales\\n🏭 Tailored machines for small workshops to large factories.\\n\\n🌍 Worldwide shipping and support\\n🚚 Global delivery, installation, and after-sales service.\\n\\nReady to upgrade your jewelry manufacturing process?\\nExplore our advanced machinery solutions at Hitesh Malviya Industries and experience the difference that precision and performance can make.\\n\"}]}","html":"

In today’s fast-paced jewelry industry, precision, automation, and durability are essential for maintaining quality and meeting demand. At Hitesh Malviya Industries, we specialize in manufacturing high-performance jewelry machinery designed to transform traditional production methods.


Our rolling mills and wire drawing machines are engineered with micron-level accuracy, delivering flawless results for gold, silver, and alloy processing. Each machine is constructed using heavy-duty materials to ensure long-lasting performance, even under continuous operation.


By integrating semi-automatic and motorized systems, we bridge the gap between craftsmanship and technology. Our machines feature smart control systems that increase productivity while minimizing manual labor—making them ideal for modern jewelers.


With over 25 years of experience, we offer customized machinery solutions tailored to specific manufacturing needs. Whether you're a small workshop or a large-scale factory, our equipment is built to improve efficiency and reduce production time.


We also provide global support, including shipping, on-site installation, and after-sales service to ensure seamless operation across borders.


Why Choose Us?


✅ Precision-built jewelry machinery

🛠️ Crafted with micron-level accuracy for flawless results.


💪 Durable and reliable design

🔩 Built to withstand continuous, heavy-duty use.


⚙️ Automation for efficient production

📈 Boosts productivity with minimal manual effort.


🧩 Custom solutions for all scales

🏭 Tailored machines for small workshops to large factories.


🌍 Worldwide shipping and support

🚚 Global delivery, installation, and after-sales service.


Ready to upgrade your jewelry manufacturing process?

Explore our advanced machinery solutions at Hitesh Malviya Industries and experience the difference that precision and performance can make.

"}
